x.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iUq4jNtsL2jU/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iUq4jNtsL2jU/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" width="530" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;霍尔木兹海峡的卫星视图。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：Gallo Images&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普打击伊朗的决定&lt;/strong&gt;给世界很大一部分石油供应带来了新的风险。伊斯兰共和国本身的产量占全球产量的 3% 以上，使其成为欧佩克第四大生产国，但由于其战略位置而&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/qFtwRdoiJTe1YVHUgPGg8VhvjFhG1ovdp0J9yrULUrIAzZ299Rje00Djln0WzJfRIf40772Ux6Ji_XSmHpqJXGEfqdaz-4NIjtS_GMPymI-6IA-a8iB-DCfau6kphe2DJIf7ngX1mWUXDk5mtuqyuS5mhZ4SHHZmkICk-bVUFKsPBUgWUyv7pvxbQMhUdzVMl9dtH0zU-uFdhh6hHsEGCA4DGfVfYNpgNU0EEcRx34bU9uaMvXicxijc93fbzQ08R3EkBYmu7Xpdog01pcaC-_3IoVBk0FYfa_WRYZC9X-ERFBJYRTrbfY-rEsNi4fHdNea5j6P9TmxELtTMB2EKkmpJ0JKhl3n3KBFdkOuGChaXpIt3CV5GlrQzYS4/jph6s24C_cFd6hshy1RJGScbAjk18x8k/18" target="_blank"&gt;拥有更大的影响力&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;伊朗位于霍尔木兹海峡的一侧&lt;/strong&gt;，霍尔木兹海峡是输送世界五分之一石油和大量天然气的咽喉要道。现在，由于&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ucTmvPdyzzOGRqsOfifgKgE0T5w5SWk2T0zQoXtMJd1sijYpj4qRqb4teqqRZLuhA88g1nmBo0n0w3mXCpdB4fX1Xy3UvPSNwneRWRDEIkOXDz_qOhWI7njXa3lAW8jLFHmgzamiWd7USq_XCSRR3VpFKXfBU2bSygauTgGpu1HjrEX8xVRvNan-WrAMxbbhqYIMW_JbEOQ8zlIocq6BP6dchIIlFM0TpxlN6StueVT0Ya70H8WRGwMx609pZ7CfCJtXwXBaMTQGOWLbaeozdlq3bG5rxgzl4xllfeChLx5vnL6lvF6gxCdavXxgK-cwDmGLPadTn8oqhO-E9Gm146_Y2O3USo3JNEAWCp-IhPt5CfKekgweIbJScvo/KMak7Dh0tlQoJl0S2JlyyVeNMc8TB0C3/18" target="_blank"&gt;通过海峡的油轮运输&lt;/a&gt;基本停止，石油价格出现四年来最大涨幅。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;数十艘满载油轮&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ePwgy3bIGGT2F7-XazPhyNyMtVyMwwhU41MYdjkHG9Ktw1sEEB65LJKR7kbyRDP9h6v7FdslJD9rZqDpjIRyLe-bewncJ7jRfQtFBcJBdzDKiOPxiPk8RJDber0yK59J3-WhkCduzPz3bAn-MbXurvuW9H4KD7BXNHZzhgt6fOIfEOa5L8t5g1XVmHNUALakl8_8xeJknlxqBcOGAVoXJXysHDFLsl-Qkbc-eqrnPz55gyamNfpmUf6sh0PNv9Fyy5Og04BYtpojprH3vWcvHqpbkgAbnnyqrg8ZCJhUwAqNW2LygZanOMM-KCMUAeosrAMm9Co3XbCSOeSUg0wW6w1K-858MTwBTG_bqUeot-w1L56sgyzczb4nsSs/bSrWrnEeLqeEgTnrYlOpOg4L_HLu0RAC/18" target="_blank"&gt;正滞留在波斯湾&lt;/a&gt;，中东主要产油国可能&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/3QlspTM7JaIu8eElvYgWuN1fIy176qGe6BAZsE5apZe5UcRIgNTrxZS_Rwl6AmBXNg6V9luD896Cl0zLLaomnWtnoNa75pjjncqcIWTcxWIrC-oiy5nj9sOBh1247hcf22ngkXmYcEyeka5kE8lTEM_YVfXtEIlR_3oTjpZab2MxSp66DXMRbv9my2XQofFeBsACeIo8SMWfgbsm-GWUWbL7YNPA75QfBa2tjdw1nxjXEUW8fn8tGdHFq-JAZV__e1haITofQgc71scC5UUEf6O2zIl1VBQPPc9VrmX1PvSdcscqCFP6yb2sryjFzEXFcW-Ks-yTHix9Xej6L6GvssNPE0JOMP_mhnukqCubAkSQ4PkzZG5hi6dLL1k/26E_UWdFeY5gzSbjGBLYxNmkdcoImdLy/18" target="_blank"&gt;被迫暂停生产&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;尽管 OPEC+ 同意&lt;/strong&gt;以稍微加快的速度恢复石油产量增长，但许多&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/FXVvQLy-jRO0RO32Dk91pVbsPvt-bSXkxzLjSXb5FMDb53umAFibjfNluWD-nyJvjRI4aKc4IYQhC-OZTg-X0IGTNt-aeIg2RZF-gkcFLNxW0CeB6xQFUPN1K6-q3RTwVdBSkdRdn3W0gwM8WPWS00uNmXyaE6vy0UYwqRfm1YOlHlZasSOK3wTldAuGsIsVnc9f3J1PHT1qF_DcRckpjdHdWKaRrF_eVMBZpScL1bslbj-SjjRWwD1w_bJN8cdOTrJSlWxQkXn-sviJevFjP2sgENc1tq4seRPWVP8AA1eBpE3e-Bc8Y7lIPkaRz9mqdu0m5gBxGN-O9OZH_vP-kUP_WcMCGqUPsEC4BIY7zboDeYFhAJk77aCt7ek/m3CkeSc41noW5tqicdf8j71Oc-OtqB6-/18" target="_blank"&gt;生产商开采更多石油的能力有限&lt;/a&gt;，而且&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/TfLfyeE0245sEM4HTABkYC3qb8s2chzQ0lHTNLMKk8H5wgc7JwSLApQOM5mzBcKd_v7ak9bxeCBPXc